# Git / IDE
# Keep `tools/` out of ignore — Docker builder needs `tools/i18n/source/*.ts` for `npm run i18n:compile`.
.git
.github
.cursor
**/.DS_Store

# Optional local monorepo checkouts / huge trees (not part of DO GitHub context; keep tar small)
external

# Dependencies & build outputs (reinstalled / rebuilt in image)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
build
*/build
**/.turbo

# Tests & Playwright (not needed for production image)
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/playwright/.cache
nursenest-core/tests

# Logs & env (never bake secrets)
**/*.log
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Misc caches
**/.eslintcache
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
